2013-01-21|2013-01-27.description: The Chaotix travel the world in search of Mighty and Ray! The trail leads them to Sand Blast City and into the clutches of the nefarious Sand Blasters. The case takes a turn for the secretive as lies are spun and plans are hatched. And Mighty makes an all-or-nothing decision!
2013-01-21|2013-01-27.name: All For One Part 3: Deep Cover

2013-01-28|2013-02-03.description: Richie Rich is back for another collection of classic-style stories! We start off with an all-new story by Richie Rich's co-creator, Sid Jacobson, and follow that up with digitally re-colored reprints of Richie Rich adventures, including the classic "The Mad Mad Big Big Race"! It's an 'amazing race' featuring Richie Rich versus his mean cousin Reggie! 28 pages in all, when adjusted for inflation, that's about a Million Laughs!

2013-02-04|2013-02-10.description:
Proper Japanese Title: ハートに火をつけて

Chapter Titles

  • Lesson 419: Set the Heart Aflame
  • Lesson 420: Climbing the Stairway of Adulthood Means Being Confined and Unable to Rise
  • Lesson 421: Romantic Love and Parental Affection
  • Lesson 422: Bald Dad, Grey Haired Dad, and Glasses Dad
  • Lesson 423: No One Is Interested In License Photos
  • Lesson 424: 3000 Leagues In Search of Scabbard
  • Lesson 425: Total Sadist vs Total Sadist
  • Lesson 426: Both Idiots and Katana Have Their Uses
  • Lesson 427: Realistically Spiral Turds Have A Maximum of Two Full Twists
2013-02-04|2013-02-10.name: Set the Heart Aflame

2013-04-22|2013-04-28.description: In part 2 of "Orpheus in the Underworld," Tom's quest for Lizzie has hit a major hurdle, in that he no longer remembers who either of them is. But is it possible he's already found her without even realizing it? And who holds the true power in Hades, where masks may hide anything-or nothing?
2013-04-22|2013-04-28.name: Orpheus in the Underworld, Part 2 of 3

2013-04-29|2013-05-05.description: "Unlucky 13" part 1 of 1! Batman doesn't believe in luck, but when he takes one of Gotham's unluckiest criminals into protective custody, Thirteen forces him to reconsider.
2013-04-29|2013-05-05.name: Unlucky Thirteen

2013-05-06|2013-05-12.description:
A 'Fear Itself' chapter! Elektra and the Shroud battle the sinister Killgrave as the escaped supervillains run riot! Meanwhile, Misty Knight faces her greatest fear! By Dan Abnett, Andy Lanning and Kyle Hotz!

Veil makes a dramatic decision – and Avengers Academy changes forever! By Christos Gage and Tom Raney!

Includes material previously published in Heroes for Hire #11-12 and Avengers Academy #20.

2013-05-27|2013-06-02.description: There's a price on Gabbatha's head and the Silencer means to collect.
2013-05-27|2013-06-02.name: Sleeping Partners, Part Seven: Have No Fear of Mad Elephants

2013-07-08|2013-07-14.description: Best frenemies Veronica & Betty have been fighting over Archie for over 70 years! You've always known, however, that Veronica's the one who should come out on top. She's refined, she's beautiful, and she can get Archie to drop everything for her! This 100-page digital exclusive collects some of Veronica's best victories over Betty. Join Riverdale's most vivacious vixen in the battle for Archie's heart!
2013-07-08|2013-07-14.name: Team Veronica

2013-07-15|2013-07-21.description:
A new adventure begins! Fantomex has been captured by Captain Britain and must face the harsh justice of the mystical realm called Otherworld! X-Force mounts a rescue mission and is pulled into a terrifying war!

By Rick Remender and Greg Tocchini.

Includes material reprinted from Uncanny X-Force #20-23.

2013-08-12|2013-08-18.description:
Astro Boy: The Artificial Sun concludes in this heated finale! Astro Boy returns and teams up with the human-turned-robot Holmspun! Will they be able to stop the rogue sun from frying the earth? Or with they crash and burn? Also included are Buddha, Pheonix, and Black Jack.

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: The Artifical Sun Chapter Three
  • Buddha Part Three: In the Forest of Trials Chapter Four
  • Phoenix: Future Chapter One
  • Black Jack: Tetsu of the Yamanote Line
2013-08-12|2013-08-18.name: Vol. 48

2013-08-26|2013-09-01.description:
The Phoenix is approaching Earth - and it wants Hope!

By Jason Aaron, Kieron Gillen, Matt Fraction, Jonathan Hickman, Ed Brubaker, Brian Michael Bendis, John Romita Jr. Chris Bachalo and Greg Land.

Includes material reprinted from: Wolverine & The X-Men #9, Avengers vs X-Men #1-2 and Uncanny X-Men #11

2013-09-23|2013-09-29.description: FINAL NEWBEGIN ARC CONTINUES! The branded man is at the gates! Can anything stop him? Perhaps Marcus knows more than he's letting on... Not that it will matter, if Jakob succeeds in assassinating him during the Festival! But cracks are appearing in everyone's plans, as the branded man wreaks havoc in the city, and Brother Bryn finds his faith tested... for the last time.
2013-09-23|2013-09-29.name: Watchfire

2013-10-07|2013-10-13.description:
Death Comes As the Beginning

Private eye Richard Moore has found a new line of work: ghost-busting! Hired by a wealthy man who believes he’s being haunted, Mr. Moore discovers that the ghost may not be real—but the threats of murder are. To stop the killer, Conan must uncover the truth behind a disaster that took place 13 years ago!

Then Conan helps a newscaster track down a persistent stalker, but the seemingly simple case may be more than it appears. Is Conan on the trail of another of the Men in Black?
2013-10-07|2013-10-13.name: Death Comes As the Beginning
